Weather Forecast App
A dynamic web application that provides real-time weather data and a 7-day forecast for any city worldwide. Built with a focus on asynchronous programming and customizable user interface.

Live Demo: https://weather-mu-opal.vercel.app/

 Key Features
Global Search: Fetch current weather conditions and 7-day forecasts for any city around the globe.

Extended Forecast: Provides detailed weather data for the upcoming week, including temperature trends and conditions.

Multilingual Support: Easily switch between languages (English/Russian) to reach a wider audience.

Theme Switching: Includes a Dark/Light mode toggle for improved user comfort and accessibility.

Dynamic Backgrounds: (Optional, если есть) UI elements that change based on current weather conditions.

 Tech Stack
Language: JavaScript (ES6+)

Frontend: HTML5, CSS3

API: OpenWeatherMap API (or similar) for real-time meteorological data.

Deployment: Vercel

 How it Works
The app sends an asynchronous request to the weather API using the fetch method.

Data is parsed and dynamically injected into the DOM.

User preferences (language and theme) are managed through local state or localStorage.
